{"tid":1947854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有圖]上水男子危坐欄河　消防到場前墮樓喪生","createTime":"2020-03-28T14:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:54:54.000Z","uid":84668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"138f5d169150d24b07581db63c76e47a9e51204f","tid":1947854,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200328/bkn-20200328182513071-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200328%2Fbkn-20200328182513071-0328_00822_001.html&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=89611d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200328/bkn-20200328182513071-0328_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ed5cb25c189f2244680f2d0c811323a3e44e7017","tid":1947854,"uid":84668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"上水男子危坐欄河 消防到場前墮樓喪生<br />\n03月28日(六) 18:25<br />\n<br />\n管理員用圍板將死者遺體圍封。<br />\n1/2<br />\n上水發生墮樓事件。今日(28日)傍晚6時許，一名男子坐在上水彩園邨彩湖樓高層走廊欄河上，街坊見狀立即報案。惟該名男子突然一躍而下直跌落地面，身體重創昏迷不醒。救護員接報趕至，檢查後證實男子已死亡，管理員亦取出圍板為屍體隔開。警方於死者身上未有發現身份證明文件，現場亦沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信死者從上址一樓層大堂墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n消息指，死者是1名年約30至35歲本地男子，身高約1.7米，瘦身材，事發時身穿白色短袖上衣、黑色長牛仔褲及白色運動鞋。"},{"pid":"d62aa4c3afc21ebfbfd1c842e7015a7ca864df88","tid":1947854,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zBtuJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zBtuJ8.jpg&h=9df54886&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e49a10900bef6e1ee710be129913d5cf271323c","tid":1947854,"uid":84668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"6點幾發生既事   6:25就出到新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d939cf5cab33684bcc486fde03b62feec7d31bcf","tid":1